//
// test/sema/width/sign_extend_expr.test — sign-extend-expression
// width fixture (T024 rollover; specs/006-m3-sema/tasks.md Phase 4a).
// Per N5 (lang.ebnf:1035) the sign-extend operator `8 # sig`
// produces a sign-extended value of explicit width 8. Asserts the
// `SignExtendExpr` carries a `: BitVector(N)` Type suffix per
// `emit-ast-format.contract.md` Invariant 2.

// RUN: printf 'module m {\n  wire sig;\n  reg q = 8 # sig;\n}\n' > %t.nsl
// RUN: %nslc -emit=ast %t.nsl | FileCheck %s

// CHECK: (RegDecl {{.*}}name=q
// CHECK: (SignExtendExpr {{.*}} : BitVector({{[0-9]+}})
